N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 455.51 - Research

State Regulations

This functional reporting center must contain all the
expenses associated with the overall administrative management of all research
projects carried on by the facility. This would include all expenses associated
with all research activities that are specifically funded by internal or
external sources. (a) Standard unit of
measure. None. (b) Data source. Not
applicable. Notes
